            <p>
              ׳׳ ׳™ ׳׳׳•׳”׳‘׳× ׳‘׳×׳—׳•׳ ׳”׳–׳”. ׳׳‘׳ ׳׳”׳‘׳” ׳׳ ׳׳©׳׳׳× ׳©׳›׳¨ ׳“׳™׳¨׳”. ׳•׳׳”׳‘׳” ׳׳ ׳׳•׳׳¨׳× ׳©׳¦׳¨׳™׳›׳•׳× ׳׳©׳—׳•׳§ ׳׳•׳×׳ ׳•.
