              <p className="text-[#8B7355] text-xs">׳¢׳¨׳‘׳•׳× ׳”׳—׳–׳¨ ׳׳׳ 14 ׳™׳•׳. ׳‘׳׳™ ׳¡׳™׳›׳•׳.</p>
